{"tid":1748013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"只要殺哂啲內奸，忠臣就會打救世界㗎喇","createTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T00:38:52.000Z","uid":153938,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c05656331b688d83cb75285f23994b53bed4d0a","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"上網玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三國殺</span></span></strong>，9人標準模式，我抽中咗做<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">君主</span></span></strong>。一開局，2個忠臣斷咗線，得返1個忠臣1個內奸。輸唔緊要，打返場好波嘛。好死唔死，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">兩條友之前有仇</span></span></strong>，反賊都未死就喺度互劈。反賊佔盡上風，但兩個有理冇理，先安內後攘外。劈下劈下，死剩一個，聲稱自己係忠臣。但死咗嗰個就指控佢係內奸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>反賊仲有4個，內奸都好，合作住先啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>反賊明刀明槍，起碼係真小人。內奸呢啲扮正義嘅偽君子，最難提防啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>但我連佢係咪內奸都......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>所以咪話<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">偽君子衰過真小人</span></span></strong>囉。你畀人洗腦喇！你冇見到佢之前劈過我咩？你冇見到佢亂出牌益對家咩？呢啲仲唔係二五仔？老實講，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">佢衰過反賊啊！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>咁佢的確係豬...... 但而家死剩佢喎。就當佢係內奸會放暗箭喇，而家<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">明刀明槍都擋唔住</span></span></strong>，我殺埋佢，點夠反賊打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>反賊見到二五仔失手，自己再出手就冇人可以抵賴，自然會收歛㗎喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>乜有得咁玩㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反賊擺明想劈死我㗎喎。你而家喺場外諗下計仔好喎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>我死咗咪因爲個二五仔囉。你救唔到我就係因為個二五仔分薄哂啲資源，等你以為有得打。要贏，你首先就要劈死佢。呢一刻，未到對付反賊嘅時候啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>喂你教我點樣一個人頂住班反賊先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</strong></span>二五仔畀你劈死咗，知道冇得呃飯食，下局就唔敢落場。到時我再取代佢位置，咪幫到你劈死哂啲反賊囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">下局？反賊贏咗仲同唔同我玩，下局有冇畀人閂電制，我仲係咪你隊友都成問題啊。</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日我要建制輸啊！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0734ccb8c165829b8772dd98decc5fd8635d7fbc","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(1/10)"},{"pid":"34f64825fa65181cc91722a6ab2a10b489745f97","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(2/10)"},{"pid":"643baeec744b568f37ea36dcfcbaf79d588b80e9","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(3/10)"},{"pid":"2e187c5ffbe65df402eaff9918195f0e28d73241","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(4/10)"},{"pid":"9f391e013c5b5ce0e3ed8cf8193f99455c6ea2f1","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(5/10)"},{"pid":"588658e440d020016773c8ad21a5b1221fdfac2e","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(6/10)"},{"pid":"3db9c8068c4c2f6f7e92ceb6027d326f414cbb61","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(7/10)"},{"pid":"c652ad8e391925e9461ff6a4d229b2abb03f8d68","tid":1748013,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸"},{"pid":"5e14536ccc4df37a3b0c920e9ced2adae6947b67","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(8/10)"},{"pid":"7f8c6e1761b6eefe68e6aa92eebabf5086eca37a","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(9/10)"},{"pid":"12497c7ab0e777a0de47388b1dcc3857b41ec2aa","tid":1748013,"uid":3677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"30c05df4f53e668e07c1fcf249d25532db072e41","tid":1748013,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"聽日我要建制輸(10/10)"},{"pid":"66d62b378347ee5ed1d935f19f4a4f6ff3e71e94","tid":1748013,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"敵人既敵人就係朋友, 打機就緊要合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947051fa78b5807420efe26a84578998b6465f84","tid":1748013,"uid":10653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"唔需要諗當唔當內奸係朋友<br />\n總之呢個局勢 就需要利用內奸嚟除反賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ad3c5080f6bcf1057abaa1d150742902535cd3","tid":1748013,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"重要post無人推?"}]}